flowchart TD
    A[LLM Planner Output] --> B[Queue Ingestion + Idempotency + DAG Validation]

    B --> C{Mutability?}

    C -->|readonly| D[queued - readonly]
    C -->|mutating| E[queued - mutating]

    D --> F[ready]

    E --> G[Preflight L1 - Schema Validation cached command-schema singleton sync io-free]
    G --> L1{Schema valid?}
    L1 -->|no - schema error| OSE[failed - hard block schema error]
    L1 -->|yes| D2[Preflight L2 - Domain Checks parallel conflict permission precondition timeout 500ms]
    D2 --> D3[Preflight Layer 3: Execution Gate]
    D3 --> PFC[PreflightResult contract status pass soft block hard block retry hint blocking layer retry after ms retry count duration ms]

    PFC --> PS{PreflightResult.status}
    PS -->|pass| AC{autoconfirmmode active?}
    PS -->|soft block| U[clarification returned via ai send message]
    PS -->|soft block issue code domain conflict| DC[blocked confirmation - domain]
    PS -->|hard block| O[failed - terminal]
    PS -->|retry hint| PG[Preflight retry gate]

    AC -->|yes| F
    AC -->|no| I[blocked confirmation - awaiting confirm]
    I --> TTL{blocked confirmation TTL expired?}
    TTL -->|yes| BTF[failed - blocked timeout]
    TTL -->|no| J[User Confirm or Clarification]
    J --> F

    PG --> PFR{retry count < max retries? max retries 4}
    PFR -->|yes| PBO[retry waiting with retry after ms and persisted backoff ms formula]
    PBO --> F
    PFR -->|no| OPR[failed - hard block max retries exceeded]

    DC --> TTL

    F --> DEPCHECK{depends on failed item?}
    DEPCHECK -->|yes| SK[skipped - terminal]
    DEPCHECK -->|no| SL{Scheduler-Lock - max 1 running per thread id}
    SL -->|slot free| K[running]
    SL -->|slot occupied| F

    K --> L{Execution Result}

    L -->|success| M[succeeded]
    L -->|transient error - provider timeout or io| N[retry waiting]
    N --> RB{retry count < max retries?}
    RB -->|yes| BO[Backoff + jitter + next retry at]
    BO --> F
    RB -->|no| RF[failed - retry exhausted]
    L -->|contract repair - CONTRACT issue codes| RP[Neuer Queue-Eintrag mit depends on]
    RP --> QDAG{depends on DAG valid?}
    QDAG -->|yes| B
    QDAG -->|no| CYF[failed - dependency cycle]
    L -->|domain error - recoverable| P[failed - execution failure + Observation with error detail]

    M --> OB[Observation Builder]
    P --> OB
    O --> OB
    OPR --> OB
    OSE --> OB
    BTF --> OB
    RF --> OB
    CYF --> OB
    U --> OB
    SK --> OB

    OB --> RR{Repair needed?}
    RR -->|yes| BG1{Budget guard before repair LLM call?}
    BG1 -->|no| FAIL[failed - budget exceeded]
    BG1 -->|yes - LLM emits new command| B
    RR -->|no| LS{Max loop steps budget ok?}
    LS -->|exhausted| FAIL
    LS -->|ok| GR{Goal reached?}

    GR -->|yes| S[Final Synthesis]
    GR -->|no| BG2{Budget guard before re-plan LLM call?}
    BG2 -->|no| FAIL
    BG2 -->|yes| T[Re-Plan: new LLM step - nur anhaengen - simple retrieval - kein neuer initialer Catalog Embedding Start]
    T --> B

    AL[(audit log: every state transition)]
    B -.-> AL
    G -.-> AL
    D2 -.-> AL
    D3 -.-> AL
    PFC -.-> AL
    L -.-> AL
    OB -.-> AL
    FAIL -.-> AL
    S -.-> AL

